            , and divers other persons, whose names are unknown, being respectively subjects of our Lord the King, constituting a society or partnership called or known by the name of the British Fire Assurance-office, carrying on the business of insuring houses and other property from loss or damage by fire.</p>
               <p>3d COUNT, the same as the first, but with intent to defraud William Agnew, James West, and James Henry Deacon, being respectively subjects of our Lord the King.</p>
               <p>4th COUNT, the same as the first, but with intent to defraud 
               <persName id="t18261026-54-victim441" type="victimName">
                  John Thomas Barber 
                  Beaumont
